# Update Category/SubCategory Audience. 
Updates the audience of Category in Knowledge Library.

**Usage**  
`POST https://graph.workplace.com/{{category-id}}`

**Parameters**
* `read_audience`: The audience persmissions for the Category.


**Usage**
Provide the details of read_audience to set the permissions.
```
POST https://graph.workplace.com/{{category-id}}
Body:
  //Example 1:
 {
   "read_audience": {
        "audience_type": "PROFILE_FIELDS",
        "profile_set_conditions": [
            {
                "field": "LOCATION",
                "operator": "CONTAINS",
                "values": [
                    "London",
                    "San Francisco"
                ]
            },
            {
               "field": "TITLE",
                "operator": "CONTAINS",
                "values": [
                    "Engineer"
                ]
            }
        ]
    }
}

  //Example 2:
  {
 "read_audience": {
        "audience_type": "GROUPS",
        "groups": [{group_id_1},{group_id_2}]
    }
}

  //Example 3:
  //Only for subcategories to inherit the parent category's audience
 {
   "read_audience": {
        "audience_type": "INHERIT" 
    }
}
```

